{"tid":1479020,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人因為今次社運而有精神病","createTime":"2019-08-16T17:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T03:26:31.000Z","uid":25162,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7325252cb5486c39420942c18cdd1d098d5013","tid":1479020,"uid":25162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"屋企有人（深藍到on9） 由7月開始就好似痴左線咁<br />\n日日係咁睇住啲直播 <br />\n不停鬧 鬧晒所有示威者<br />\n幾毒既野都講晒<br />\n<br />\n當嘗試叫佢冷靜 佢會鬧埋你<br />\n鬧得更痴線<br />\n<br />\n雙眼好似想殺左人咁<br />\n好恐怖 好心寒<br />\n但痴線既人只會覺得全世界都係癲 唯我獨醒 <br />\n唔會肯睇醫生/停止再睇live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己係黃 已經有因為呢啲嘈過 <br />\n但發現同個痴撚線既人討論係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"561a70bc1a641c494a1e5dca42b0ca3ea4c738a9","tid":1479020,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:37:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">加</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">油</span>"},{"pid":"94cce599b90f722c0bb68aa05cb269a88aea1bab","tid":1479020,"uid":307619,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:41:02.000Z","msg":"睇字都覺得樓主好辛苦"},{"pid":"d3f79c4573244ed6c9828c0698845fb47b7ca822","tid":1479020,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:41:21.000Z","msg":"我都有，所以而家黐撚咗線咁要攬炒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[寧鳴而死！]All in 攬炒好似係唯一嘅出路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476343</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bd1c585a3fdb291b3f3b6dce14b544b851c43a2e","tid":1479020,"uid":279995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:42:21.000Z","msg":"一齊加油"},{"pid":"7d67ecd12443f361f84dd81f49e429f9cbc5caa9","tid":1479020,"uid":307195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T17:47:30.000Z"